sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Route as RayCluster Route<br/>TLS Edge Termination
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: User Accesses Ray Dashboard

    User->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Route: Forward request<br/>TLS Edge Termination
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+

    alt User not authenticated
        OAuth->>OAuthServer: Redirect for authentication<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        OAuthServer->>User: Login page
        User->>OAuthServer: Credentials
        OAuthServer->>OAuth: OAuth token (cookie)
    end

    OAuth->>Dashboard: HTTP/8265<br/>No encryption (localhost)
    Dashboard-->>OAuth: Dashboard HTML
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard page

%%------------------------------------

    participant User2 as User/Dashboard
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CFWebhook as CodeFlare Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CFOperator as CodeFlare Operator<br/>Controller
    participant KROperator as KubeRay Operator

    Note over User2,KROperator: Flow 2: RayCluster Creation and Security Setup

    User2->>API: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>CFWebhook: Mutate webhook call<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS 1.2+<br/>mTLS
    CFWebhook->>API: Injected OAuth/mTLS config
    API->>CFOperator: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (Operator SA)

    CFOperator->>API: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    CFOperator->>API: Create Route/Ingress<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    CFOperator->>API: Create OAuth ServiceAccount<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    CFOperator->>API: Create OAuth ClusterRoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    CFOperator->>API: Create mTLS CA Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token

    KROperator->>API: Create Ray Head Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (KubeRay SA)
    KROperator->>API: Create Ray Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token

%%------------------------------------

    participant User3 as User
    participant API2 as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AWWebhook as AppWrapper Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CFOp as CodeFlare Operator
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller

    Note over User3,Kueue: Flow 3: AppWrapper Admission and Workload Scheduling

    User3->>API2: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    API2->>AWWebhook: Mutate/validate webhook<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS 1.2+<br/>mTLS
    AWWebhook->>API2: Validated AppWrapper
    API2->>CFOp: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token

    CFOp->>API2: Create Kueue Workload CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    Kueue->>API2: Watch Workload<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    Kueue->>API2: Update Workload status (Admitted)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token

    CFOp->>API2: Watch Workload admission
    CFOp->>API2: Deploy wrapped resources<br/>(RayCluster/Job/PyTorchJob)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token

%%------------------------------------

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>openshift-monitoring
    participant MetricsSvc as Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Prom,RayHead: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>MetricsSvc: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    MetricsSvc-->>Prom: Operator metrics<br/>(Prometheus format)

    Prom->>RayHead: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No auth
    RayHead-->>Prom: Ray cluster metrics
